IHS Concept\",\"seo_description\":\"A project under the Hotel scheme must absolutely be approved by the Board of Investment.\"},\"submit\":\"save\",\"language\":\"en_US\",\"ref_from\":null,\"status\":\"published\",\"format_type\":null,\"categories\":[\"8\"],\"image\":null,\"tag\":null}', 'created', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; Intel Mac OS X 10.14; rv:73.0) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/73.0', '196.20.218.102', 1, 10, 'The IHS Concept', 'info', '2020-03-25 10:11:55', '2020-03-25 10:11:55'),
