(3, 'About us', '<h4><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><b>1. COMPANY</b><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong> PROFILE</strong></span></span></h4>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"lrg-txt\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Island Homes is a real estate listings marketplace for the &nbsp;property industry in Mauritius.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"lrg-txt\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">We serve the informational needs (<i>Property Listings</i>, <i>Market Data</i> and <i>Industry News</i>) of a fragmented addressable local real estate industry.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"lrg-txt\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Our platform is to display, host and market Residential, Commercial, Vacation and Land listings currently For Sale, Rent, Auction and Exchange&nbsp; each month.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"lrg-txt\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Islandhomes. is openly available for all real estate market participants to <i>Search, Engage, Connect and Transact</i> with any active property listing in Mauritius&ndash; anytime.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"lrg-txt\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">At our core &ndash; it&rsquo;s all about presenting accurate and easily accessible real estate listings data, actionable market intelligence and correlated sector news &ndash; all on one platform (ours) &ndash; to help people worldwide easily find properties of their liking in Mauritius. And once found, help them make more informed property transaction decisions, all on a scale.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">With the slogan &quot;Breaking time, through space&quot; with a sustainable development strategy, taking Real Estate as a focus area, Island Homes is constantly connecting between buyers and sellers in the field of Real estate, bringing people closer together, over the distance of time and space, is a reliable place for real estate investment - an area that is constantly evolving over time.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<h2 style=\"font-style: italic; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color:#16a085;\">&quot;Breaking time, through space&quot;</span></span></strong></span></h2>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</h4>\r\n\r\n<h4><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">We make real estate simple and exciting for our stakeholders such as other&nbsp; real estate agents companies, owners, buyers by creating simple tools and CRM that&nbsp; provide key information and simplify transactions.</span></h4>\r\n\r\n<h4><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><b><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\">2. VISION&nbsp;</font></b></span></h4>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">- Acquiring domestic areas.<br />\r\n- Reaching far across continents.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h4><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><b>3. MISSION</b></span></h4>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">- Creating the community<br />\r\n- Building destinations<br />\r\n- Nurture happiness</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 1, NULL, 'default', 0, 'Founded on August 28, 1993 (formerly known as Truong Thinh Phat Construction Co., Ltd.), Flex Home operates in the field of real estate business, building villas for rent.\r\nWith the slogan \"Breaking time, through space\" with a sustainable development strategy, taking Real Estate as a focus area, Flex Home is constantly connecting between buyers and sellers in the field.', 'published', '2019-11-27 01:52:36', '2020-03-29 07:43:08'),
